<template>
  <el-table
    :data="tableData"
    stripe="true"
    style="width: 100%">
    <el-table-column
      prop="date"
      label="日期"
      width="180">
    </el-table-column>
    <el-table-column
      prop="name"
      label="姓名"
      width="180">
    </el-table-column>
    <el-table-column
      prop="address"
      label="地址">
    </el-table-column>
  </el-table>
</template>

<script>

    data() {
      return {

        }, {

          name: '王小虎',
          address: '上海市普陀区金沙江路 1517 弄'
        }, {
          date: '2016-05-01',
          name: '王小虎',
          address: '上海市普陀区金沙江路 1519 弄'
        }, {
          date: '2016-05-03',
          name: '王小虎',
          address: '上海市普陀区金沙江路 1516 弄'
        }]
      }
    }
  }
</script>
